# RPG Stations - avatarCustomization-namespace additions, en-US (authoritative).
# This file's basename targets Hytale's own "avatarCustomization" language namespace (the
# namespace the client's emote UI reads emote names from - vanilla emotes use
# avatarCustomization.emotes.<Id>.name). Server-shipped .lang files merge per-key-additively
# into a namespace, so this file adds ONLY brand-new keys for this mod's own EmoteAssets
# (Server/Emote/*.json) and never overrides a client-owned one.

emotes.RPG_Emote_Saw.name = Sawing
